des:
You can simply ask Alexa to control your fan. After connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our German Pool Smart Control app in app market then register an account;
(2). Configure our devices in our Smart Control app and change appropriate name for your devices;
(3). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android, IOS or Amazon app market then configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(4). Search Smart Control skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(5). Enable Smart Control skill, and you'll be navigated to Smart Control login page;
(6). Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(7). Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on the fan.”
“Alexa, turn off the fan.”
